{"tid":2167573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愛豆團太不容易了！ITZY的刀群舞怎麼來的？一天練舞8小時，練到全身發抖！","createTime":"2020-08-21T07:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T10:23:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e58f57452b40c861bf909e8a5d93c5816b178b8b","tid":2167573,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"女團的「刀群舞」氣場完全不輸男團，最近回歸的ITZY就完美展示了這一點。<br />\n<br />\nITZY帶著新曲《Not Shy》回歸，通過YouTube頻道向粉絲們展現了華麗的回歸舞台，強勁有力又整齊劃一的舞蹈看得人移不開視線，只想感歎「舞台炸裂」。<br />\n<br />\n成員們配合完美，不停變換的走位都無法改變她們整齊的動作，如同複製粘貼一般，驗證了ITZY是「刀群舞」女團的稱號。 都說台上一分鐘台下十年功，為了將動作誤差減至最小，成員們私下也花費了不少功夫。<br />\n<br />\n禮志最近亮相某廣播節目中就透露，每天都要花7、8個小時練舞，有娜也稱一開始身體無法適應，經常跳到全身發抖。<br />\n<br />\nITZY「怪物新人」的稱號絕對不是隨便就得來的，背後是成員們辛勤刻苦的努力。<br />\n<br />\n最後來一起欣賞一下ITZY的最新歌曲吧~。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SD0-owuwDpE&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSD0-owuwDpE%26feature%3Demb_title&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuzk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=3b940694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SD0-owuwDpE&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"4364524f9e10466fe6827cce2a28250c28f2315c","tid":2167573,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:00:40.000Z","msg":"辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497a6e366dd9767028ebd10b398bc6556277a673","tid":2167573,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"充滿血汗淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f48449e10b3cae82b70b050a99fe607cc9c949f","tid":2167573,"uid":367089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"勁舞團唔係浪得虛名"},